{"tid":261111,"cid":25,"subCid":0,"title":"隻衰貓唔肯畀人剪指甲 點搞","createTime":"2017-05-28T07:43:01.000Z","updateTime":"2017-05-29T05:32:40.000Z","uid":18989,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"50d4dd2fdd264a25d108d96a0e7e5d123d20390f","tid":261111,"uid":18989,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-28T07:43:01.000Z","msg":"隻貓係我女朋友養 都養咗幾年<br />\n次次同佢剪都要幾條友合力捉住佢再剪<br />\n<br />\n之前我無上去幫手 佢搞唔掂好耐都無剪 結果長得滯吉到肉 要去睇獸醫<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n幫佢剪嗰陣個獸醫同姑娘都畀佢咬到+抓到<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n貓抓板佢完全唔用 鍾意抓D令面嘅木 但係完全唔覺有磨到抓<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n大家幫貓剪指甲嘅時候有咩秘訣<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"96111dcb18803821fc529d11aa3dea7bd6766458","tid":261111,"uid":18989,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-28T07:45:05.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"http://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/05/28/154437_5ef7f5ba696f16b5abf1f911d042371d.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F05%2F28%2F154437_5ef7f5ba696f16b5abf1f911d042371d.jpg&h=2efbaedf&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"http://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/05/28/154437_b6a805226a4e58d48916f96875b2e75d.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F05%2F28%2F154437_b6a805226a4e58d48916f96875b2e75d.jpg&h=c858d733&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n睇下佢幾串<br />\n一見到指甲鉗就無人捉到佢"},{"pid":"8bff45468bad217ce94a92845fa3eb223ae83a09","tid":261111,"uid":25468,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-28T07:47:37.000Z","msg":"我果隻一路剪一路怪叫 , 間中會逃走<br />\n<br />\n利申 , 由bb 開始有剪"},{"pid":"ba59